'''巨無霸地球'''（mega-Earth）的定義是質量至少是[[地球|地球]]10倍的岩石質類地[[太陽系外行星|太陽系外行星]]。巨無霸地球的質量較[[超級地球|超級地球]]（質量為地球5到10倍的[[類地行星|類地行星]]或[[海洋行星|海洋行星]]）更大。「巨無霸地球」一詞於2014年發現系外行星[[克卜勒-10c|克卜勒-10c]]時首次出現。該行星的質量相當於[[海王星|海王星]]，但是密度卻高於地球<ref>Sasselov, Dimitar (2 June 2014) [http://aas.org/media-press/archived-aas-press-conference-webcasts Exoplanets: From Exhilarating to Exasperating] {{Wayback|url=http://aas.org/media-press/archived-aas-press-conference-webcasts |date=20150920060415 }}, 22:59, Kepler-10c: The "Mega-Earth", [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t6x29ntnQb0 YouTube] {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t6x29ntnQb0 |date=20180107205418 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cfa.harvard.edu/news/2014-14|title=Astronomers Find a New Type of Planet: The "Mega-Earth"2014-14|work=www.cfa.harvard.edu/|access-date=2016-04-25|archive-date=2019-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190518164043/https://www.cfa.harvard.edu/news/2014-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="harps">[http://arxiv.org/abs/1405.7881 The Kepler-10 planetary system revisited by HARPS-N: A hot rocky world and a solid Neptune-mass planet] {{Wayback|url=http://arxiv.org/abs/1405.7881 |date=20150524030732 }}, Xavier Dumusque, Aldo S. Bonomo, Raphaelle D. Haywood, Luca Malavolta, Damien Segransan, Lars A. Buchhave, Andrew Collier Cameron, David W. Latham, Emilio Molinari, Francesco Pepe, Stephane Udry, David Charbonneau, Rosario Cosentino, Courtney D. Dressing, Pedro Figueira, Aldo F. M. Fiorenzano, Sara Gettel, Avet Harutyunyan, Keith Horne, Mercedes Lopez-Morales, Christophe Lovis, Michel Mayor, Giusi Micela, Fatemeh Motalebi, Valerio Nascimbeni, David F. Phillips, Giampaolo Piotto, Don Pollacco, Didier Queloz, Ken Rice, Dimitar Sasselov, Alessandro Sozzetti, Andrew Szentgyorgyi, Chris Watson, (Submitted on 30 May 2014)</ref>。

